DESCRIPTION: This function initializes a JPype connection and starts Ghidra in headless mode, allowing direct import of 'ghidra' and 'java' modules without setting up projects or programs.
SOURCE: https://github.com/NationalSecurityAgency/ghidra/blob/master/Ghidra/Features/PyGhidra/src/main/py/README.md#2025-04-06_snippet_0

