TITLE: Initializing MicrosoftDemangler Class in Java for Ghidra
DESCRIPTION: Defines the MicrosoftDemangler class, which extends the AbstractDemangler class from Ghidra. It sets up the demangler with specific options and initializes necessary components for name demangling.
