TITLE: Building PostgreSQL Object Files for Ghidra Analysis in Linux/macOS
DESCRIPTION: Script to build PostgreSQL, extract object files of appropriate sizes, and prepare them for analysis in Ghidra. This includes compiling with debug information and stripping the final executable.
