TITLE: Implementing strnlen Stub using Sleigh - Target Override Technique
DESCRIPTION: A Sleigh implementation that replaces the target of external strnlen calls by implementing the full function including proper stack management and return handling.
SOURCE: https://github.com/NationalSecurityAgency/ghidra/blob/master/GhidraDocs/GhidraClass/Debugger/B2-Emulation.md#2025-04-06_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: sleigh
CODE:
```
RAX = 0;
<loop>
if (*:1 (RDI+RAX) == 0 || RAX >= RSI) goto <exit>;
RAX = RAX + 1;
goto <loop>;
<exit>
RIP = *:8 RSP;
RSP = RSP + 8;
return [RIP];
```

